title: As long as I breath
description:
As long as I breath

genre:horror/black comedy

running time:60min

extra:incl 20 min making of/bloopers

made in the summer 07 by the amateur movie makers Rottensoulz

check out our website www.rottensoulz.com for some teasers or on youtube


Nicke and Lukas wants to bring their homie Frans on an quiet peaceful campingtrip.

It all starts so great and they are having a great time until......

Hell breaks loose and they must fight to the last breath.


Incl cover(nero)
